Subject: Secunia Research: Symantec Mail Security Folio
	Flat File Parsing	Buffer Overflows

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 08/04/2008

 - Symantec Mail Security Folio Flat File Parsing Buffer Overflows -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

